Affected version:
1.5.0-617

Fixed version:
N/A

Commit fix:
The maintainer said that one of the previous commit fixed this issue. It needs a bisect.

Credit:
This bug was discovered by Agostino Sarubbo of Gentoo.

CVE:
CVE-2017-14644

